@startuml akdb-document-lifecycle
title AKDB - DB-Native Architecture Document Lifecycle
[*] --> Draft : upsert document
Draft --> Current : sections/decisions complete
Current --> Current : DB-native edit
Current --> Exported : deterministic export
Exported --> Current : next DB-native edit
Exported --> Verified : repeat export + tests + drift checks
Verified --> Current : architecture/code change
Current --> Superseded : replacement accepted
Draft --> Deleted : explicit delete
Superseded --> Deleted : explicit cleanup
Deleted --> [*]
note right of Exported
Exported Markdown and PlantUML are projections.
They are never the edit/import loop for this project.
end note
@enduml
